<doc id="1160535" wikidata="Q922328" url="?curid=1160535" title="Masahiko Tanaka">
<text>is a Japanese actor and voice actor. He is known for voicing Gauron from &quot;Full Metal Panic!&quot;, Ryo Mashiba from &quot;Hajime no Ippo&quot;, and Kyoichi Sudo from &quot;Initial D&quot;.

==Filmography==
